4:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Bojxona kalkulyatori 2026-yilgi haqiqiy sxemaga keltirildi: boj 15% (yangi) / 40% (ishlatilgan) + sm³ uchun 0,4–1,0 $, to'g'ri utilizatsiya yig'imi va ro'yxatga olish (~13 BHM). Elektromobil importiga imtiyoz 2030-yilgacha."}]
5:["$","article","3",{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-5","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-foreground leading-snug mb-1.5","children":"Soliqlar: QQS bo'sag'asi, norezident JShShS, to'lov muddatlari"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"QQS va soddalashtirilgan soliqqa ro'yxatdan o'tish bo'sag'asi — 1 mlrd so'm aylanma. Norezident JShShS — 12% (20% edi). Mol-mulk, yer va transport solig'ini jismoniy shaxslar 15 aprel va 15 oktyabrgacha to'laydi. Zararlarni o'tkazish — muddat cheklovisiz."}]]}]
6:["$","article","4",{"className":"rounded-xl border border-border bg-card p-5","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-foreground leading-snug mb-1.5","children":"Mehnat va ijtimoiy: ta'til, kasallik varaqasi, aliment, pensiya"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Eng kam ta'til — 21 kalendar kun, 9 bayram kuni, ortiqcha ish soatining yillik chegarasi bekor qilindi. Kasallik varaqasi: 8 yilgacha — 60%, undan ortiq — 80%. Aliment — MROTning kamida 26,5%; 2 yoshgacha bola parvarishi nafaqasi — MROTning 60%. Eng kam pensiya — 2026-yil 1-iyuldan 983 000 so'm."}]]}]
